Palm 
<normalizedToken id="1B4C04C5A5E65E759AF7F185E813ECFF" originalValue="CaÃ±on">Canon</normalizedToken>
, Angel de la Guardia, Golf of California, Mexico. Type depository: California Academy of Sciences (CASC).
